{"tid":134414,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)朱千雪親身教授極速減肥5大法!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-25T12:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T09:27:33.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a70e20442375523846ac42d16ea4c95bf50c8ee","tid":134414,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63028/58af9e9b641d5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63028%2F58af9e9b641d5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=167e2654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡通片拍攝真人版並不是新鮮事，而日本經典卡通《櫻桃小丸子》的真人版電視劇也曾經上映，但選用成人演員飾演的《小丸子》真人版你又會否有興趣？台灣有電視台拍攝了一部中文版的《小丸子》電視劇，劇中所有角色全部由成人演員擔任，將於 3 月起播放。<br />\n<br />\n▼《櫻桃小丸子》的演員皆是成人，要如何演出國小學生的童真感是一大難題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63028/58afa10897f82.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63028%2F58afa10897f82.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c4658f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼《櫻桃小丸子》裡的經典角色：班長丸尾、美環、花輪都會出現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63028/58afa1095f7cf.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63028%2F58afa1095f7cf.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2a76bf4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yHfQZmlEGA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyHfQZmlEGA8&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e64fec7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yHfQZmlEGA8</a><br />\n日前電視台釋出一條 6 分鐘長的預告片，據知劇中的演員全部由日方版權商和作者櫻桃子親子挑選和確認，每個造型都參照足卡通中的細節，飾演主角小丸子的是新人演員林芯蕾，花輪同學是汪東城，而跟作者櫻桃子關係不錯的王友良則飾演大野同學。"},{"pid":"e5608476acb41dbf11b1959389d8d38884e688c5","tid":134414,"uid":49392,"like":0,"disli